response.overview: Alex is not just any Police Dog he is THE Police Dog. A gruff little good boy who is one bone away from being a bad boi. Will the hard knock LA crime scene force Alex to leave his faith behind or will he be told by his owner that he's not an real cop, he's just been forced to wear a dog police costume and that all the film equipment and crew are evidence that this is all fake.
response.title: Alex the Police Dog
